<h1>Guide to the Best Restaurants in Orlando</h1>

<p>Here are places I've eaten in the greater Orlando area, and enjoyed and/or gotten food poisoning from.</p>

<table>
	<tr>
		<th>Name</th>
		<th>Address</th>
		<th># of Reviews</th>
	</tr>
	<% @restaurants.each do |restaurant| %>
		<tr>
			<td><%= link_to restaurant.name, restaurant %></td>
			<td><%= restaurant.address %></td>
			<td><%= restaurant.reviews.length %></td>
		</tr>	
	<% end %>
</table>
